---
title: Palak Tofu Curry with Basmati Rice and Crispy Onions
description: 'Palak' is Hindi for spinach, the iron-rich leafy green in this mildly spiced, creamy curry - not to be confused with 'saag', which means any kind of leafy greens! Firm tofu, made from compressed soybeans, is the perfect vehicle for soaking up the delicious flavours.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R22_W35_UK_V22131-8_main_high-3f197eb5.jpg
